Mbali Ngiba, bụ onye ome ihe nkiri na onye na-agụ egwú South Africa
N'afọ 2013, o mere mpụta mbụ telivishọn na ọrụ nke "Linda" na Mzansi Magic anthology miniseries Abangani
N'otu afọ ahụ, ọ rụrụ ọrụ na fim ntinye ozugbo na vidiyo The Right na ọrụ ngosipụta dị ka"Zodwa". Mgbe ahụ ọ rụrụ ọrụ cameo  Generations
N'afọ 2016, o sonyeere Mzansi Magic telenovela Greed & Desire wee rụọ ọrụ "Welile"
Mgbe nke ahụ gasịrị, ọ rụrụ obere ọrụ "Emergency Nurse" na ihe nkiri e.tv Easy Money
Na 2018, o sonyeere na oge nke abụọ nke Mzansi Magic telenovela Isithembiso ka ọ rụọ ọrụ "Buhle"
N'otu afọ ahụ, o mere obere ọrụ "Lab Technician" na Mzansi Magic telenovela ozo The River
ihe nkiri ahụike Durban Gen wee gosiputa ọrụ nke " Oriakụ Mthembu ".
